Safe Calculator that does all the calculations using only bitwise operators.
Safe integer calculator - warns if an overflow or underflow error occurs
Simply run the program.

Looks like

Safe Integer Calculator
+ x to add
- x to subtract
* x to multiply
/ x to divide
% x to modulus
~ x to negate
^ x to raise by power x
c x to clear result
q x to quit

res = 0 >


res = 0 > (operators) (NUMBER)
and to quit simply type q.